    "The final consistency percentage was calculated by dividing the total consistency points by the maximum possible points (number of questions x 5).",
    "We also analyzed the standard deviation of agreement scores to assess response variability.",
    "We employed a multi-layered approach to ensure data privacy and security when using Azure OpenAI for sensitive healthcare data.",
